      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/will-putin-use-nuclear-weapons-what-russia-s-doctrine-change-means</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯军事策略的显著特点就是不排除在常规战争中使用核武器。]]></description>
